<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1753] Deadlock in client using deprecated APIs in a multi-threaded application</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1753</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is a deadlock somewhere in HTable or HConnectionManager when using the deprecated API in a multi-threaded application.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I haven&apos;t had a chance to look at the thread dump in detail yet, but will attach it to this issue&lt;/p&gt;</description>
